(self.webpackChunk_N_E=self.webpackChunk_N_E||[]).push([[867],{9692:function(e,t,i){Promise.resolve().then(i.bind(i,4070))},4070:function(e,t,i){"use strict";i.r(t),i.d(t,{default:function(){return a}});var o=i(7437);i(2265);var r=i(9003),n=i(8468);function a(){let{lang:e}=(0,n.Z)(),t="fr"===e;return(0,o.jsx)(r.Z,{title:"TalentGrid",image:"/assets/projects/Logo_black.png",logoStyle:"object-contain bg-white p-4",context:t?"En tant que candidat, j'ai identifi\xe9 des frictions majeures dans le recrutement traditionnel. Le d\xe9calage entre formation et emploi, combin\xe9 aux limites d'un CV d'une page, cr\xe9e des inefficacit\xe9s pour les \xe9tudiants, universit\xe9s et recruteurs. TalentGrid est n\xe9 de ce besoin d'un e-portfolio riche, interactif et exploitable.":"As a candidate navigating the job market, I identified critical pain points in the traditional recruitment ecosystem. The disconnect between education and employment, combined with the severe limitations of CV-based hiring—where candidates are reduced to a single page of text—created significant challenges for students, universities, and employers. This exploratory project emerged from recognizing the need for a comprehensive, data-rich e-portfolio system that serves as a complete CV replacement, showcasing projects, skills, and experiences in a rich, interactive format.",objective:t?"Cr\xe9er une plateforme tripartite (universit\xe9s, \xe9tudiants, entreprises) pour remplacer la logique CV par un profil complet fond\xe9 sur projets, comp\xe9tences et preuves.":"To revolutionize the connection between education and employment through a three-sided platform that creates value for universities, students, and employers. The core goal was to completely replace traditional CV-based hiring with a unified, data-rich e-portfolio solution that serves as a comprehensive showcase of candidates' work, addressing critical pain points across the recruitment ecosystem.",implementation:t?"J'ai pilot\xe9 TalentGrid en tant que project manager, en collaboration avec Om Dighe sur la supervision de production. Nous avons con\xe7u une plateforme qui transforme la d\xe9couverte et l'\xe9valuation des talents, centr\xe9e sur un builder no-code d'e-portfolios.":"I served as the project manager for TalentGrid, working closely with my associate Om Dighe who supervised production. Together, we developed a platform that transforms how talent is discovered, evaluated, and connected to opportunities. The centerpiece of our solution is a no-code e-portfolio builder that generates rich, interactive portfolios serving as complete CV replacements, combining no-code technology with specialized recruitment methodology.",method:t?"La plateforme fonctionne comme une marketplace tripartite :\n\n• Universit\xe9s : outil d'administration externe sans int\xe9gration IT lourde, activation automatis\xe9e des \xe9tudiants en fin de cursus, modernisation des services carri\xe8re.\n\n• \xc9tudiants & dipl\xf4m\xe9s : cr\xe9ation no-code d'e-portfolios complets en remplacement du CV, chatbot IA pour l'engagement recruteur, abonnement accessible.\n\n• Entreprises : acc\xe8s \xe0 des viviers pr\xe9-qualifi\xe9s, profils riches avec profondeur de lecture (5-10 min), mod\xe8le de pricing \xe0 la r\xe9ussite du recrutement.":"The platform operates as a three-sided marketplace:\n\n• For Universities: External administration tool requiring no IT integration, automated student engagement system targeting final-year students, and modern career services offering enhancing graduate outcomes.\n\n• For Students & Graduates: No-code ePortfolio creation with comprehensive project showcasing that completely replaces traditional CVs, AI-powered chatbot to engage recruiters, and affordable subscription pricing.\n\n• For Companies: Access to pre-qualified talent pools from partner universities, rich candidate profiles with 5-10 minute reading depth (replacing one-page CVs with comprehensive e-portfolios), and value-based pricing model paid only upon successful hire with a 360-day attribution window.",result:t?"TalentGrid d\xe9montre une solution compl\xe8te pour fluidifier la transition formation-emploi : e-portfolios v\xe9rifi\xe9s, shortlists qualifi\xe9es et meilleure qualit\xe9 de matching. La strat\xe9gie de d\xe9ploiement pr\xe9voit d'abord l'activation des universit\xe9s, puis l'acquisition employeurs.":"TalentGrid successfully demonstrates a comprehensive solution that transforms education-to-employment transitions. The platform replaces traditional CVs with rich, verified ePortfolios and generic job boards with tailored shortlists, creating exceptional value for all stakeholders. The phased rollout strategy prioritizes university partnerships to establish the talent pool foundation, followed by employer recruitment to generate revenue through placements, with sustainable recurring revenue from student subscriptions.",tools:["No-Code Platform","AI Chatbot","ePortfolio System","Three-Sided Marketplace","Project Management"],screenshots:[{title:t?"Dashboard candidat":"Candidate Dashboard",image:"/assets/projects/screenshots/StudentDash.png",description:t?"Le dashboard \xe9tudiant permet de cr\xe9er et g\xe9rer un e-portfolio complet via un builder no-code. Il remplace le CV traditionnel en valorisant projets, exp\xe9riences et comp\xe9tences dans un format riche.":"The student dashboard provides candidates with a no-code e-portfolio builder to create and manage their comprehensive e-portfolios. This system completely replaces traditional CVs by allowing students to showcase their projects, experiences, and skills in a rich, interactive format that provides recruiters with a complete view of their capabilities."},{title:t?"E-portfolio g\xe9n\xe9r\xe9":"E-Portfolio Generated",image:"/assets/projects/screenshots/Render.png",description:t?"Exemple d'e-portfolio g\xe9n\xe9r\xe9 pr\xe9sentant projets et comp\xe9tences dans un format complet et interactif, offrant aux recruteurs une vision nettement plus riche qu'un CV une page.":"An example of a generated e-portfolio showcasing a candidate's projects and skills in a rich, comprehensive format. This interactive portfolio serves as a complete CV replacement, providing recruiters with detailed insights into a candidate's work, achievements, and capabilities—far beyond what a traditional one-page CV can convey."},{title:t?"Dashboard \xe9coles":"Schools Dashboard",image:"/assets/projects/screenshots/SchoolDash.png",description:t?"Le dashboard universit\xe9 permet de suivre l'engagement \xe9tudiant, les outcomes dipl\xf4m\xe9s et l'adoption des e-portfolios sans int\xe9gration IT lourde.":"The university dashboard enables educational institutions to manage student engagement, track graduate outcomes, and provide modern career services without requiring IT integration. Universities can monitor student e-portfolio completion and help students transition from education to employment with comprehensive CV replacements."},{title:t?"Dashboard recruteurs":"Companies Recruiting Dashboard",image:"/assets/projects/screenshots/RecruteurDash.png",description:t?"Le dashboard recruteur donne acc\xe8s \xe0 des viviers pr\xe9-qualifi\xe9s et \xe0 des profils riches permettant une \xe9valuation plus fine des candidats.":"The recruiter dashboard provides companies with access to pre-qualified talent pools and rich candidate e-portfolios that replace traditional CVs. Recruiters can efficiently discover and evaluate candidates through comprehensive profiles that showcase projects, skills, and experiences in detail, enabling better hiring decisions."}]})}}},function(e){e.O(0,[699,509,145,3,971,117,744],function(){return e(e.s=9692)}),_N_E=e.O()}]);